videos.title: Leyline Axe is a Balanced Embercleave
videos.description:
Embercleave was absurdly busted so Leyline Axe is a more balanced version! Is Embercleave's little brother good enough to bring Boros equipments into Standard?.... probably not...but it is fun.

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

videos.description:
